      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Keyed via Symbol.for('three-flatland.registry') so double-bundled module copies still share. Cross-realm separation is fundamental — not solved by any pattern.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Keyed via Symbol.for('three-flatland.registry') so double-bundled module copies still share. Cross-realm separation is fundamental — not solved by any pattern.",
